    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313480/extras/15cffb9e967fa8ef50e254dc1d078b08.poster.avif?t=1761678103\" width=616 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313480/extras/15cffb9e967fa8ef50e254dc1d078b08.webm?t=1761678103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313480/extras/15cffb9e967fa8ef50e254dc1d078b08.mp4?t=1761678103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Based on Real Events</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In  2015, an Argentine lawyer was found dead in his home after making a few powerful enemies. Some say that he committed suicide, and others say that he was silenced. The truth behind his death has been lost... or has it? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Continue the investigation in <i>After Death</i>: a first-person horror game based on this mysterious death. Some say that our developers have gotten an insider's peek into the investigations that went on behind this incident... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313480/extras/75039ddd9573c653fdd08c256a5d8c7c.poster.avif?t=1761678103\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313480/extras/75039ddd9573c653fdd08c256a5d8c7c.webm?t=1761678103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313480/extras/75039ddd9573c653fdd08c256a5d8c7c.mp4?t=1761678103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Investigate a Strange World</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are Prosecutor Bisman. After a sudden death, you wake up as a ghost<i> </i>in a police station where the Grim Reaper himself roams the corridors. Speak to the only living man in prison who can see you, help the other ghosts trapped there, and maybe someone will help you to get your memories back...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313480/extras/a438e2c56d9cd97169aa9e1f928dbb22.poster.avif?t=1761678103\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313480/extras/a438e2c56d9cd97169aa9e1f928dbb22.webm?t=1761678103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313480/extras/a438e2c56d9cd97169aa9e1f928dbb22.mp4?t=1761678103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Classic Horror Elements:</strong> The Grim Reaper is always lurking around the corner, watching and waiting... Can you avoid his grasp?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Meaningful Choices:</strong> Change the fate of different characters in the story with your decisions. Will you be their hope or their doom?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Complex Narrative:</strong> Build a complete picture of your own murder case by experiencing multiple endings, each revealing new information. Gather all the clues and find a way to finally rest in peace.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313480/extras/88e0acadae1f5b2d8d817e5f1b388fbe.poster.avif?t=1761678103\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313480/extras/88e0acadae1f5b2d8d817e5f1b388fbe.webm?t=1761678103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313480/extras/88e0acadae1f5b2d8d817e5f1b388fbe.mp4?t=1761678103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
